[Amit Varma]: just from his writing, but his way of thinking about a subject. All of us, we dig deep as

00:01:54.500 --> 00:01:58.760
[Amit Varma]: far as our capacity allows, and then we stop. And the narratives we have are the narratives

00:01:58.760 --> 00:02:03.600
[Amit Varma]: we have. But Pratap digs deeper into whatever subject he cares about and keeps himself open

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:08.600
[Amit Varma]: more than anyone else I know. Whenever I read him or interact with him, I feel like I need

00:02:08.600 --> 00:02:14.280
[Amit Varma]: to step back and learn that all my reading so far is inadequate. He was my guest in episode

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:19.200
[Amit Varma]: 186 of the show, and many people still refer to that as their favorite episode. Do listen

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:23.960
[Amit Varma]: to that if you haven't already. These two are like companion conversations in a sense.

